it.emarolab.owloop.descriptor.construction.descriptorGround

Class DescriptorGround<J extends org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.emarolab.owloop.descriptor.construction.descriptorGround.DescriptorGround<J>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Axiom, Axiom.Descriptor<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,J>, Axiom.Ground<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,J>, DescriptorGroundInterface<J>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClassGround, DataPropertyGround, IndividualGround, ObjectPropertyGround

    public abstract class DescriptorGround<J extends org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObject>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Axiom.Descriptor<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,J>, DescriptorGroundInterface<J>
    This abstract class describes common constructors and initialisations for a specific GroundInstance. All constructors fully initialise a new Axiom.Ground (i.e., set both an ontology and an instance). By default, this class takes an ontology from a file and initialises the PelletReasoner (If another OWLReferences is instantiated with the same ontoName then this ontology will be used.).
